		<tr>
		    <td valign="top">
		     <p><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Article Title:</b>&nbsp;</font>
		     <font face="Verdana" size="2">Patch - Thursday, March 7th</font><br>
		     <a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=561844" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		
		<tr><td>&nbsp;</tr><tr>
		
		    <td valign="top"><div style= "padding:4;float: right"> <script language=JavaScript src=http://www.obsidian-tech.com/absolutebm/abmx.aspx?z=26></script></div><p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    <blockquote>
Thursday Patch
<p>
This from the scheduled downtime page: 
<P>
On Thursday, March 7th, at 3AM PST, (11AM GMT), all servers will be brought down for a scheduled patch. The estimated downtime is 6 hours.<P>
- The EverQuest Operations Team
</blockquote>
